<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Portable Charger PCB Project</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0b1221; 
            color: #94a3b8;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Fixed Border Frame */
        body::after {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            border: 12px solid #1e293b; 
            pointer-events: none; 
            z-index: 9999;
        }

        /* Section Dividers - Floating Lines */
        .divider-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #0b1221;
        }

        .line {
            width: 80%; /* Does not touch the borders */
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #1e293b;
            border: none;
        }

        section {
            min-height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 80px 60px;
        }

        .text-content {
            max-width: 750px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Underlined Titles */
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #f1f5f9; 
            display: inline-block;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #1e293b; /* Professional underline */
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 0.01em;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .image-split {
            display: flex;
            padding: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #0b1221; 
        }

        .button-img {
            flex: 1;
            height: 100vh;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            /* RESIZE BOXES TO FIT IMAGES: Ensures full visibility */
            background-size: contain; 
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-color: #0b1221;
            padding: 40px; /* Inset from the edge */
            transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), filter 0.4s ease;
        }

        .button-img:hover {
            filter: brightness(1.1) contrast(1.05);
            transform: scale(1.03);
            z-index: 10;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body::after { border-width: 8px; }
            section { padding: 60px 30px; }
            h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .image-split { flex-direction: column; }
            .button-img { height: 50vh; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section>
        <div class="text-content">
            <h1>PCB Design</h1>
            <p>To create the portable charger, I decided to integrate a TP4056 breakout board and 3v-5v Buck Boost Converter using a custom-designed Battery holder PCB to ensure protection against overcharging and a smooth lithium ion charging experience. Below are renders of the AutoDesk PCB models and physical PCB models.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="divider-container"><hr class="line"></div>

    <section class="image-split">
        <button class="button-img" style="background-image: url('/images/bat-render.png'); background-size: 75%;" ></button>
        <button class="button-img" style="background-image: url('/images/physical-pcb.jpeg'); background-size: contain;" ></button>
    </section>

    <div class="divider-container"><hr class="line"></div>

    <section>
        <div class="text-content">
            <h1>Challenges Faced</h1>
            <p>During the creation of the Battery Holder PCB I ran into several problems including IC design in Eagle electronics and manufacturing issues with JLCPCB.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="divider-container"><hr class="line"></div>

    <section class="image-split">
    <div class="nested-vertical-split">
        <button class="button-img" style="background-image: url('/images/JLC-issue.png'); background-size: 180%;"></button>

        <hr class="inner-line"> <button class="button-img" style="background-image: url('/images/failed-ic.png'); background-size: cover;"></button>
    </div>

    <button class="button-img" style="background-image: url('/images/physical-pcb.jpeg'); background-size: contain;"></button>
    </section>

</body>
</html>